"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-10-minister-advocates-review-of-federations-constitutions-after-disastrous-olympics-outing\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  The Minister of Sports Development, John Enoh, has stated that there will be stiffer scrutiny of the constitutions governing Nigeria's sporting federations in advance of the forthcoming elections.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 55, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Enoh\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\"}, {\"begin\": 144, \"end\": 151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9999998339319656, \"rank\": 1.660636781805268e-07, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This announcement follows Team Nigeria's disappointing performance at the 2024 Paris Olympics, where the country did not secure any medal.\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9999998339319656, \"rank\": 1.660636781805268e-07, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enoh, speaking from Paris, stated, \\\"We did everything as a Ministry to prepare the athletes adequately and provide them with every financial support, unfortunately the performance has not produced any podium finish.\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 377, \"end\": 382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999594856577916, \"rank\": 4.051598363334018e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As we go back home, we must do everything to prevent future occurrence of the Paris disaster and if this will entail the review of how people are elected to lead our sporting Federations, it will be done.\\\"\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999594856577916, \"rank\": 4.051598363334018e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was disclosed in a statement by Diana-Mary Nsan, S.A. Media to the Minister, on Friday.\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Emphasizing the importance of upcoming federations' elections, Enoh noted, \\\"I know that elections into the Federations are coming and it will be the perfect platform to get only those who have something to offer to lead the various sports.\\\"\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on the complexity of the elections, he added, \\\"I am aware that the Sports Federations Elections in Nigeria are even tougher than our National Elections and you will begin to ask yourself why is it so?\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9999998339319656, \"rank\": 1.660636781805268e-07, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So for me as a Minister, it is important I supervise elections where only the best hands will lead the various Federations and I also understand that in some of the Federations, their constitutions will need to be reviewed for better inclusion.\\\"\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1577, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"El-Kanemi Warriors get N35.2m reward for President Federation Cup success  Transfer: Five more top players could leave Chelsea [See list]  Tinubu's Minister's WhatsApp number hacked  2024 Olympics: Minister John Enoh calls for reforms in sports administration  Olympics: Sack Sports Minister John Enoh, probe Ministry - Adeyanju writes Tinubu  Olympics: Nigerian only participated in sports that do not need investment - Seun Kuti  Paris 2024: D'Tigress Kalu named to Olympics' basketball second team  Paris 2024: You have brought joy to Nigerians - Sports Minister hails D'Tigress, Favour Ofili  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1579, \"end\": 1597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El-Kanemi_Warriors_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"El-Kanemi Warriors\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El-Kanemi_Warriors_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El-Kanemi_Warriors_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1738, \"end\": 1746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9999918522805692, \"rank\": 8.147785906963709e-06, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}, {\"begin\": 1786, \"end\": 1795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Enoh\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\"}, {\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Enoh\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\"}, {\"begin\": 1933, \"end\": 1941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.9999933756222388, \"rank\": 6.624420292014852e-06, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}, {\"begin\": 2081, \"end\": 2091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999994585804517, \"rank\": 5.414199494096206e-07, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2151, \"end\": 2160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"D'Tigress\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_basketball_team\"}]}]}"